  abstract = {Systematically evaluates the effect of sensor type (accelerometer vs. gyroscope), sensor position (ankle, back, wrist), activity type, dataset, and ML model on FOG detection. Finds ankle sensors best, accelerometer-only sufficient, and XGBoost optimal trade-off between accuracy and computational cost.},
